description.text:
Define the vendor's registered Private Enterprise Number as maintained by IANA.
				Available starting with HLT API 3.90. Valid when port_role is 'access';
				dhcpv6_hosts_enable is 1; ip_cp is 'ipv6_cp' or 'dual_stack';
				dhcp6_pd_client_range_duid_type is 'duid_en'.

Define the DHCP unique identifier type.
				Available starting with HLT API 3.90. Valid when port_role is 'access';
				dhcpv6_hosts_enable is 1; ip_cp is 'ipv6_cp' or 'dual_stack'.
